      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a> * Pawn Structure</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:344px;\"><a href=\"http://www.elke-rehder.de/Chess_Paintings.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9c/Elke_Rehder_Chess_Schach_Bauern_Pawns_Chain.jpg/342px-Elke_Rehder_Chess_Schach_Bauern_Pawns_Chain.jpg\" width=\"342\" height=\"259\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/9/9c/Elke_Rehder_Chess_Schach_Bauern_Pawns_Chain.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Elke_Rehder_Chess_Schach_Bauern_Pawns_Chain.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Arts#Rehder\" title=\"Arts\">Elke Rehder</a>, Chain of Pawns <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Pawn structure</b> is a term used to describe the positions of all the pawns on the board, ignoring all other pieces. Pawn structure encompasses a broad range of ideas, from the general shape of the pawns (such as closed or open) to specific characteristics of individual pawns.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Hashing_Pawns\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Hashing Pawns</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Standard_Terms\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Standard Terms</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Single_Pawn\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Single Pawn</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Groups_of_Pawns\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Groups of Pawns</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#General\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">General</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Dependent_on_Pawn_Structure\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Dependent on Pawn Structure</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hashing_Pawns\">Hashing Pawns</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Hashing Pawns\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><i>see main article <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></i>\n</p><p>Full evaluation of pawn structure might be quite expensive. To speed up the evaluation, many programs use a separate <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">pawn hash table</a>, addressed by a special key derived from the pawn's (and possibly also king's) position. Since pawn structure changes rather slowly, hit rate for such table is typically above 95%. Anything strictly pawn related can be stored in this hash table, including <a href=\"/King_Safety#PawnShield\" title=\"King Safety\">pawn shield</a> terms to be used dynamically for <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">king safety</a>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Standard_Terms\">Standard Terms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Standard Terms\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Single_Pawn\">Single Pawn</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Single Pawn\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Backward_Pawn\" title=\"Backward Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Doubled_Pawn\" title=\"Doubled Pawn\">Doubled Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Faker\" title=\"Faker\">Faker</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hidden_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Hidden Passed Pawn\">Hidden Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Isolated_Pawn\" title=\"Isolated Pawn\">Isolated Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sentry\" title=\"Sentry\">Sentry</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Groups_of_Pawns\">Groups of Pawns</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Groups of Pawns\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Blockage_Detection\" title=\"Blockage Detection\">Blockage Detection</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Connected_Pawns\" title=\"Connected Pawns\">Connected Pawns</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hanging_Pawns\" title=\"Hanging Pawns\">Hanging Pawns</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Minority_Attack\" title=\"Minority Attack\">Minority Attack</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Chain\" title=\"Pawn Chain\">Pawn Chain</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Islands\" title=\"Pawn Islands\">Pawn Islands</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Majority\" title=\"Pawn Majority\">Pawn Majority</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"General\">General</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: General\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Holes\" title=\"Holes\">Holes</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Center\" title=\"Pawn Center\">Pawn Center</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Race\" title=\"Pawn Race\">Pawn Race</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Weak_Pawns\" title=\"Weak Pawns\">Weak Pawns</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dependent_on_Pawn_Structure\">Dependent on Pawn Structure</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Dependent on Pawn Structure\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bad_Bishop\" title=\"Bad Bishop\">Bad Bishop</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Color_Weakness\" title=\"Color Weakness\">Color Weakness</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Pawn_Tropism\" title=\"King Pawn Tropism\">King Pawn Tropism</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/King_Safety#PawnShield\" title=\"King Safety\">Pawn Shield</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/King_Safety#PawnStorm\" title=\"King Safety\">Pawn Storm</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Outposts\" title=\"Outposts\">Outposts</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rook_on_Open_File\" title=\"Rook on Open File\">Rook on (Semi) Open File</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/CPW-Engine_eval\" title=\"CPW-Engine eval\">CPW-Engine_eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Pattern_and_Properties\" title=\"Pawn Pattern and Properties\">Pawn Pattern and Properties</a> pawn structure aspects concerning <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboards</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Levers_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Levers (Bitboards)\">Pawn Levers (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Rams_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Rams (Bitboards)\">Pawn Rams (Bitboards)</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Strategy\" title=\"Strategy\">Strategy</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hans_Kmoch\" title=\"Hans Kmoch\">Hans Kmoch</a> (<b>1959, 1990</b>). <i>Pawn Power in Chess</i>. 1959 McKay, 1990 Dover</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrew_Soltis\">Andrew Soltis</a> (<b>1976, 1995, 2013</b>). <i>Pawn Structure Chess</i>. Tartan Books, 1995 McKay, 2013 Batsford Chess <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Soei_Tan\" title=\"Soei Tan\">Soei Tan</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i>Describing Pawn Structures.</i> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Chess_1\" title=\"Advances in Computer Chess 1\">Advances in Computer Chess 1</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Danny_Kopec\" title=\"Danny Kopec\">Danny Kopec</a> (<b>1977</b>). <i>Recent developments in computer chess</i>, in Firbush News 7 Edinburgh: Machine Intelligence Research Unit, <a href=\"/University_of_Edinburgh\" title=\"University of Edinburgh\">University of Edinburgh</a> (ed. <a href=\"/Donald_Michie\" title=\"Donald Michie\">D. Michie</a>), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sci.brooklyn.cuny.edu/%7Ekopec/Publications/Publications/O_45_AI.pdf\">pdg</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rci.rutgers.edu/~goeller/\">Michael Goeller</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Pawn Battle Rules and Strategies</i>.<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.kenilworthchessclub.org/media/Pawn_Battle_Strategies.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Pawns</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Pawns-Lyudmil-Tsvetkov-ebook/dp/B074S2MYQV\">amazon</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=271055\">how to detect information about pawn structure based on bitboard</a> by <a href=\"/Uri_Blass\" title=\"Uri Blass\">Uri Blass</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=383014\">pawn structure, pawn hash, square-of-pawn, pawn-races</a> by <a href=\"/Stuart_Cracraft\" title=\"Stuart Cracraft\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52609\">Double levers</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53507\">Some more pawns</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 31, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55214\">Binders</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 04, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55290\">En passant bonus</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/En_passant\" title=\"En passant\">En passant</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55292\">Pawn checks and center levers</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55319\">Kind of backward</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  February 13, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55343\">Double pawn push</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  February 14, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56191\">Lever evaluation</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 01, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Levers_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Levers (Bitboards)\">Pawn Levers (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56206\">Chain, duo, connected</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 02, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Chain\" title=\"Pawn Chain\">Pawn Chain</a>, <a href=\"/Duo_Trio_Quart_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Duo Trio Quart (Bitboards)\">Duo Trio Quart (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56213\">Some more pawns</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 03, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56282\">Assorted tweaks</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 08, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57949\">A possible new pawn structure evaluation term?</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81rp%C3%A1d_Rusz\" title=\"Árpád Rusz\">Árpád Rusz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2015</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73629\">Pawn structure tuning</a> by <a href=\"/Vivien_Clauzon\" title=\"Vivien Clauzon\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  April 11, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a>, <a href=\"/Ethereal\" title=\"Ethereal\">Ethereal</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/Tc7XRkbRrSs/x9tUlRK1AgAJ\">Re: Tcec season 18</a> by <a href=\"/Warren_D._Smith\" title=\"Warren D. Smith\">Warren D. Smith</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, June 28, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Center\" title=\"Pawn Center\">Pawn Center</a>, <a href=\"/TCEC_Season_18#Sufi63\" title=\"TCEC Season 18\">TCEC Season 18 Sufi Game 63 10... c4</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pawn_structure\">Pawn structure from Wikipedia</a>, pattern of common <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chess_opening\">chess openings</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mark-weeks.com/aboutcom/aa03j11.htm\">Positional Play&#160;: Pawn Structure</a> by <a href=\"/Mark_Weeks\" title=\"Mark Weeks\">Mark Weeks</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawn_Structure&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.elke-rehder.de/Chess_Paintings.htm\">Chess paintings in oil on canvas</a> by <a href=\"/Arts#Rehder\" title=\"Arts\">Elke